{"tid":1744620,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"記住我地唔係要泛民贏 係要建制輸！！！！！","createTime":"2019-11-21T23:54:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-23T09:50:42.000Z","uid":42046,"like":30,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"f20daf876c00a19d1ed27d779935b4997ab6cc16","tid":1744620,"uid":42046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T23:54:28.000Z","msg":"唔想叫建制 不過咁易明d"},{"pid":"076ca29b243c9fb4e79d67946011b2df664edc14","tid":1744620,"uid":323228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f20daf876c00a19d1ed27d779935b4997ab6cc16","tid":1744620,"uid":42046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T23:54:28.000Z","msg":"唔想叫建制 不過咁易明d"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T00:19:07.000Z","msg":"大家快的麻煩連登以外幫手文宣，以下正皮、加推、幫手做，時間無多<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n出街全部對家街站，死得啦，麻煩認真幫推呢個整合左既行動PO啦，再唔做的野輸死喇：<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n【行動post】<span style=\"color: green;\">《緊急》全民選舉文宣+鍵盤戰</span><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1743618\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1743618</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">原PO<br />\n選舉文宣！文宣！文宣呀！唔夠對家多呀！的牆無曬喇！</span><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/ezmgyS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/ezmgyS</a>"},{"pid":"45827486ba5eed42798caa8f83ddd3b09f15e239","tid":1744620,"uid":42046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T00:32:25.000Z","msg":"Up"},{"pid":"4c0c0dca0cbcc9e980ecee2f6966c226ae2b7014","tid":1744620,"uid":267823,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T00:35:17.000Z","msg":"狙擊建制<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e8eba48cdf9d3779fe10fc7952a48ad8de07a76","tid":1744620,"uid":123774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T00:35:34.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>一票不投𠝹票黨<br />\n<br />\n投泛民就係確保藍閪輸</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"1eb606b50cb0849fc4721a2c52be3064101c03d2","tid":1744620,"uid":42046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T01:46:38.000Z","msg":"Up"},{"pid":"456266506a3c5487fe84bc18d309ccca4f98e761","tid":1744620,"uid":320670,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T01:55:09.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5bc21b01f69c42e65bc5683e4198b4a969d645a0","tid":1744620,"uid":42046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T02:02:43.000Z","msg":"Up"},{"pid":"fb61ea90a7a6ef9e981a23413c6f26ace1c86fd6","tid":1744620,"uid":53675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T02:04:07.000Z","msg":"係人都知一到選舉前啲分化同帶風向五毛就會出曬嚟 <br />\n轆過幾個選舉po啲仆街有兩大理據<br />\n<br />\n1 民主派出賣港人 一票不投民主派<br />\n2 唔係要焦土嘅咩 焦土就係投白票<br />\n<br />\n我想同大家講 今次選舉我哋目的只有一個 <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">不求民主派贏，只求建制派輸！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">大家手上有票唔用 人哋建制派就已經計好曬票 投白票必然唔係焦土而係放生建制派呢一點其實顯然易見 所以三毛同熱狗真係好易分得出 </span></span><br />\n<br />\n星期日可以話係藍絲最團結嘅一日 所以 我誠心懇請咁多位手足 大家可以同仇敵愾 槍口對外 目標一致咁 先踢走保皇黨 後而整頓內在 多謝各位<br />\n<br />\n光復香港 時代革命 <br />\n五大訴求 缺一不可"},{"pid":"0a82aa4f9834e225345b93a9d96754043ee568fd","tid":1744620,"uid":63192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T03:58:30.000Z","msg":"無錯, 不分化, 係要建制輸！！！！！"},{"pid":"053cfaf88b551d472f6be5e88088651931fb43d8","tid":1744620,"uid":42046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T07:44:23.000Z","msg":"Up"},{"pid":"671cdf74d63b6cc2547f0d7b017396acb4600891","tid":1744620,"uid":88133,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T07:45:09.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"41d239a6dce9d865a35516263ce164a3cd1ae493","tid":1744620,"uid":156096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T07:45:29.000Z","msg":"**** 眾籌 ****<br />\n<br />\n唔好意思，仲係要借個位&amp;幫你推推POST<br />\n<br />\n鍾庭耀教授為今次運動發起了超大型全港性民調，長期追蹤今次運動大事件的民意 &amp; 證明香港人未放棄，然後做份國際文宣 話比全世界聽：5毛網軍不代表香港人<br />\n(由於中大民調欠缺資金做今次反送中民調，我們的眾籌會同時加入新項目，籌到的款項亦會用作資助中大民調)<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">眾籌到而家先75%</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />, 仲要大家支持<br />\n<br />\n第六期民調結果POST<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1745339/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1745339/page/1</a> <span style=\"color: red;\">(new)</span><br />\n第五期民調結果POST<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1726268/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1726268/page/1</a> <br />\n第三&amp;四期民調結果POST<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1696271/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1696271/page/1</a><br />\n第二期民調結果POST <br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1686054\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1686054</a><br />\n第一期民調結果POST<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1675545\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1675545</a><br />\n<br />\n眾籌link:  <a href=\"https://www.collaction.hk/project/story/1209\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.collaction.hk%2Fproject%2Fstory%2F1209&d=t5TWSf1rAjisfLcmnBMt82qRhi9KU01BjP2Z1UqMPtI%3D&h=e71d00f6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.collaction.hk/project/story/1209</a><br />\n官方link (我們香港人計劃) :<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.pori.hk/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.pori.hk%2F&d=t5TWSf1rAjisfLcmnBMt82qRhi9KU01BjP2Z1UqMPtI%3D&h=a909d563\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.pori.hk/</a><br />\n<br />\n(對唔住，咁危難時刻下我知而家仲叫大家課金可能好反感，但我相信兄弟爬山，各有各做，行得通就全力去做<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)"},{"pid":"1dd7e1917ba83016ca139a1cf5c8be05bef75152","tid":1744620,"uid":61396,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f20daf876c00a19d1ed27d779935b4997ab6cc16","tid":1744620,"uid":42046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T23:54:28.000Z","msg":"唔想叫建制 不過咁易明d"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T07:46:28.000Z","msg":"土共"},{"pid":"f439e18748f4c4ef12872f3de7c943c6eb792cb3","tid":1744620,"uid":208744,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T08:07:52.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">TLDR: 同你男女朋友屋企人講為咗我投XX好唔好？</span><br />\n<br />\n除咗我哋要出嚟投票之外，爭取中間/港豬票都好重要。對住佢哋最好就用動之以情，唔好講咁多道理。麻煩大家如果身邊有中間/港豬男女朋友或者家人，就同佢講:<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">為咗我投XX好唔好？</span><br />\n<br />\n佢唔理你就加多幾滴眼淚，七情上臉，發揮大家嘅演員才華。星期日記得同佢一齊去，確保佢有投。<br />\n<br />\n要贏一定要拎多D中間票 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n麻煩大家出力幫手<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"938535a22eac192a165e00e0b2bc0a2f920030fc","tid":1744620,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T08:30:45.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9963b032e325615125a5959cf8c582fb262d95c6","tid":1744620,"uid":42046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T09:43:25.000Z","msg":"Up"},{"pid":"035207b4948c41b30f9de834f8959c5a5febdd32","tid":1744620,"uid":288154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T09:50:42.000Z","msg":"11.24 民主歌聲獻香港 圍繞理大走一圈 【和理非行動post】<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/k8yQUK2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fk8yQUK2.png&h=727d0b17&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n等候時及面對<span style=\"color: red;\">白警</span>時唱<strong>《Sing Hallelujah To The Lord》</strong><br />\n<br />\n香港區 6:00pm 灣仔紅隧入口集合，大量兩層巴士接過紅隧，或自行行過紅隧。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">【急】請手足傳給撞區候選人！</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n必在 11月 24日 7:30am 前，在facebook發表，證明已為<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">7－11pm</span></strong>活動申請不反通知書，先發表就出線有票，遲發表要退選。</span><br />\n撞區表 <a href=\"https://hkfactcheck.io/crashes/1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhkfactcheck.io%2Fcrashes%2F1&d=t5TWSf1rAjisfLcmnBMt82qRhi9KU01BjP2Z1UqMPtI%3D&h=42dfbb50\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hkfactcheck.io/crashes/1</a><br />\n<br />\n誠邀：曾出席『<span style=\"color: red;\">民主歌聲獻中華</span>』演藝人、民主派議員、及候選人<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">光復香港 時代革命</span><br />\n<br />\n11.24 民主歌聲獻香港 圍繞理大走一圈 【和理非行動post】<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1747254\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1747254</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">幫幫手推一推行動post拉！連登重有邊個唔去投票！</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n下期預告：12.1 民主歌聲撐林夕 圍繞理大走一圈 【行動post】"}]}